<item>
            <title>[SPR-2566] &lt;form:label/&gt; should have MessageSource support</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-2566</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;(c.f. comment from Matt Raible on &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-2354&quot; title=&quot;It isn&amp;#39;t clear how to use form:label&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPR-2354&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPR-2354&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It would be cool if this tag supported a &quot;key&quot; attribute so you could read directly from your messageSource. For example:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;form:label path=&quot;firstName&quot; key=&quot;user.firstName&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Just a thought.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Matt&lt;/p&gt;</description>
